# Sales & Demand Forecasting System

A machine learning project that predicts 3 months of future retail sales 
for Electronics, Clothing, and Food & Beverage categories.

## Features
- Data cleaning and preparation
- Time-based feature engineering (lag features, seasonality, rolling averages)
- Linear Regression forecasting model
- Model evaluation (MAE, RMSE, MAPE, R²)
- Business-friendly visualizations

## Results
- Electronics MAPE: 3% (97% accuracy)
- R² Score: 0.957

## Tools Used
- Python
- Pandas, NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

## How to Run
pip install pandas numpy scikit-learn matplotlib seaborn
python3 sales_forecasting_display.py
